channel.title: How can i fix the item nulls?
channel.description: well i made an client and added models and stuff but the thing is that like tons of others items are nulls. is there any way to fix them?

item.title: How can i fix the item nulls?
item.dc:creator: @fallen543 fallen543
item.description:
@fallen543 wrote:

Your client doesnt have the items coded into them, The null’s are item id’s that havent been coded into the client, You have to add in new items and change their id’s to the null’s id to fix them.
